 Correlation functions for atmospherical data analysis.
 \emph{Q. J. Roy. Meteor. Soc} Part A \bold{125}, 2449-2464.

 \item Wendland, H. (2005) \emph{Scattered Data Approximation.}
 Cambridge Monogr. Appl. Comput. Math.
 }
}

